Use a Tabular Report in a Dashboard

You can use a tabular report as the source report for a dashboard table or chart widget if you limit the number of rows it returns.

To create a tabular report:

* Select Add | Row Limit.
* Set the row limit to 10, 25, or Custom. If custom, enter a number between 1 and 99.
* Set the sort by and sort order options.
* Click OK.
* Click Dashboard Settings in the toolbar.
* Enter a name and value to use in dashboard tables and charts.
* Click OK.

You can now use this tabular report as the source report for a dashboard widget.
title: Using Tabular Reports in Dashboards
